Feature: Contextual Translation

As a student
I want to select words within a lesson
So that I can view their immediate translation

Scenario: Display translation and pronunciation
Given the user is reading a lesson
When the user selects a word
Then the system displays the meaning of the word
And the system displays its pronunciation

Scenario: Translation unavailable
Given the selected word does not exist in the database
When the user selects the word
Then the system displays "Translation not available"
